01:11:53.640 --> 01:11:55.030
Yes?

01:11:55.030 --> 01:11:56.410
Good.

01:11:56.410 --> 01:11:57.410
Better now?

01:11:57.410 --> 01:12:01.060
Now rub My foot.

01:12:01.060 --> 01:12:03.270
Now let’s see.

01:12:03.270 --> 01:12:06.590
Yes, rub it.

01:12:06.590 --> 01:12:09.900
Rub it hard.

01:12:09.900 --> 01:12:12.110
Really hard.

01:12:12.110 --> 01:12:15.430
Rub it hard.

01:12:15.430 --> 01:12:16.530
Hard.

01:12:16.530 --> 01:12:19.850
With your fingers.

01:12:19.850 --> 01:12:20.950
Hard.

01:12:20.950 --> 01:12:23.160
You too.

01:12:23.160 --> 01:12:43.520
Press with both the hands, press with both
the hands.

01:12:43.520 --> 01:12:47.640
Void is caught, catching, Void, Void catches
with this one, the left Void.

01:12:47.640 --> 01:12:48.640
Ah!

01:12:48.640 --> 01:12:51.330
Are you relaxing now?

01:12:51.330 --> 01:12:53.540
(Seeker says yes)

01:12:53.540 --> 01:12:55.010
Very well.

01:12:55.010 --> 01:12:59.440
(Seeker says he is feeling suspicious)

01:12:59.440 --> 01:13:24.350
You are suspicious of?

01:13:24.350 --> 01:13:34.610
(Seeker: And frightened)

01:13:34.610 --> 01:13:38.510
Suspicious and?

01:13:38.510 --> 01:13:40.480
(Seeker: And frightened)

01:13:40.480 --> 01:13:41.480
Shri Mataji: Frightened of whom?

01:13:41.480 --> 01:13:42.480
(Seeker: You)

01:13:42.480 --> 01:13:43.480
Me?

01:13:43.480 --> 01:13:44.480
Why?

01:13:44.480 --> 01:13:45.480
I am not as bad as hashish is!

01:13:45.480 --> 01:13:46.480
Why are you frightened of Me?

01:13:46.480 --> 01:13:47.480
(Seeker: I had another guru)

01:13:47.480 --> 01:13:48.480
Who is he?

01:13:48.480 --> 01:13:49.480
(Maharaji)

01:13:49.480 --> 01:13:50.480
Who’s Maharaji this… you were not suspicious
of him?

01:13:50.480 --> 01:13:54.230
(I’m suspicious and over it)

01:13:54.230 --> 01:13:59.800
That’s correct, that’s good, that’s
very good.

01:13:59.800 --> 01:14:05.370
(It’s good to be suspicious of everybody)

01:14:05.370 --> 01:14:06.960
No, no.

01:14:06.960 --> 01:14:16.690
You must know who is the right and who is
the wrong type.

01:14:16.690 --> 01:14:18.220
If you are sensitive you will know yourself.

01:14:18.220 --> 01:14:21.580
What do you expect is to get your own powers,
isn’t it?

01:14:21.580 --> 01:14:28.560
To become your Self, that’s what should
help you – not all other tricks of giving experiences and this and that.

01:14:28.560 --> 01:14:31.140
You have to become your Self.

01:14:31.140 --> 01:14:32.140
Isn’t it?

01:14:32.140 --> 01:14:33.630
Like all others said.

01:14:33.630 --> 01:14:35.540
Now, there’s nothing to be suspicious about.

01:14:35.540 --> 01:14:39.460
I have not taken any money from you, nothing.

01:14:39.460 --> 01:14:41.590
Nothing selling here.

01:14:41.590 --> 01:14:42.590
See?

01:14:42.590 --> 01:14:43.590
Alright?

01:14:43.590 --> 01:14:59.890
Now, you are asking for something great, something
Self-realisation I am talking about, no experiences,

01:14:59.890 --> 01:15:02.790
it’s self-realisation.

01:15:02.790 --> 01:15:04.240
Yes?

01:15:04.240 --> 01:15:13.860
Now rub it on the Void, here.

01:15:13.860 --> 01:15:14.860
(…)

01:15:14.860 --> 01:15:19.510
Better now she?

01:15:19.510 --> 01:15:21.400
Agya?

01:15:21.400 --> 01:15:42.780
She’s never been to a guru she said.

01:15:42.780 --> 01:15:48.550
You did some pranayama also?

01:15:48.550 --> 01:15:49.550
Pranayama?

01:15:49.550 --> 01:15:50.550
Breathing?

