01:17:24.520 --> 01:17:25.520
What did you get?

01:17:25.520 --> 01:17:26.520
Nothing.

01:17:26.520 --> 01:17:28.520
(I never mistrusted him. I still don’t completely mistrust him.)

01:17:28.520 --> 01:17:29.520
You do not mistrust him.

01:17:29.520 --> 01:17:35.900
