cigarettes and why you…

01:17:39.270 --> 01:17:46.230
(Yes, he said I shouldn’t, it’s since
when I was first his devotee I didn’t smoke).

01:17:46.230 --> 01:17:49.490
Now you started smoking after becoming his
devotee.

01:17:49.490 --> 01:17:53.170
So this is the achievement.

01:17:53.170 --> 01:18:03.810
See, if you have found your Self you enjoy
your Self so much, alright?

01:18:03.810 --> 01:18:12.620
That you just don’t run away from your Self,
minimum of minimum, that should happen to you.

